OL,3,CParents beg the government not to axe
OL,4,Cdrug for children with rare condition
OL,6,FThe family of a toddler from Ramsgate
OL,7,Fin Kent who has a rare genetic
OL,8,Fcondition, say they're living in fear
OL,9,Fof her drug treatment being taken away.
OL,11,FHarper Dunsford has Spinal Muscular
OL,12,FAtrophy and only took her first steps
OL,13,Fat the age of three, after starting on
OL,14,Fthe drug Spinraza.
OL,16,FBut the government health body NICE,
OL,17,Fis currently reviewing whether it
OL,18,Fshould still be used on the NHS - due
OL,19,Fto its cost.
