OL,6,FBefore treatment, Harper had lost the
OL,7,Fability to stand and was starting to
OL,8,Fchoke because of the disease. The
OL,9,Fmuscle wasting meant the rare genetic
OL,10,Fcondition was slowly deteriorating.
OL,12,FHowever, when she started taking the
OL,13,Fdrug, her mum Mia Clark saw an
OL,14,Fimmediate change.
OL,16,FShe said: "We started to notice that
OL,17,Fshe was pulling herself up to stand
OL,18,Fagain.
