OL,6,FFor Harper's physiotherapist, Kavi
OL,7,FPunniyakotti, she believes the
OL,8,Fmedicine saves lives.
OL,10,FShe said: "The quality of life has
OL,11,Fimproved, so they can access, access
OL,12,Flots of things, they develop some
OL,13,Fmuscle strength. So they are able to
OL,14,Fmaintain postures and do some
OL,15,Fmovements with assistive devices."
OL,17,FCharities like Spinal Muscular Atrophy
OL,18,FUK fund and support research into the
OL,19,Fclinical development of drug
OL,20,Ftreatments.
