OL,6,FGiles Lomax, who is the CEO at the
OL,7,Fcharity, said: "We've amazing data.
OL,8,FWe've got real-life world stories.
OL,9,FWe've got a combination of clinicians
OL,10,Fbehind us.
OL,12,F"We've got a really, really amazing
OL,13,Fstory that tells such improvements the
OL,14,Fhistory of SMA has never seen. We need
OL,15,Fto get these approved because they
OL,16,Fwill change families' lives from now
OL,17,Fon and forever."
