OL,6,FSpeaking on the potential ban,
OL,7,FHarper's mum said: "I can't watch her
OL,8,Flose her abilities again. You know,
OL,9,Fshe's kind of she's lost them and
OL,10,Fshe's gained them.
OL,12,F"And to have them taken away again
OL,13,Fwould be because it would be imminent.
OL,14,FIt would happen immediately. The
OL,15,Ftreatment is keeping her alive."
OL,17,FNICE is due to meet next week to start
OL,18,Fdrafting its recommendations.
